<ab facs="#facs_24_r2l3">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als vns ewr gnade nehſt
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r2l4">wegen antreffende <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> Juden Joſſe . Vnd
                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Juden den Johell etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r2l5"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol
